Source: http://hdfeos.gsfc.nasa.gov/hdfeos/software/HDFEOS_5_1_6/HDFEOS%v.tar.Z
Source2: http://hdfeos.gsfc.nasa.gov/hdfeos/software/GCTP/gctp.tar
